data.description: Looking for the perfect neighborhood?  Put your finshing touches on this beautiful 4 sided brick home situated on 1.36 acre corner lot in prestious North Cedartown location! Wooded lot has alot of potenial as well as large spacious rooms with a huge, unfinshed, walkout basement! Living room/dining, large galley kitchen with breakfast area, awesome den with built-ins and fireplace, oversized master with double closets, built-ins with window seat, additional 2 bedrooms, and so much more.  Minor repairs needed, seller motivated and willing to negotiate price based on repairs needed.  Roof and a/c in great shape, large screen porch to relax for bird watching! Don't miss out of this great opportunity!
